%3BIf%20you%20pull%20apart%20the%20rose%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works%2C%20you%20ruin%20the%20rose%2C%26quot%3B%20Rock%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20responding%20to%20questions%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20VCs%20BI%20spoke%20with%20demurred%20when%20asked%20who%20they%20think%20Rock%20is%2C%20but%20some%20offered%20broad%20theories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20best%20guess%20is%20an%20associate%2FVP%20level%20at%20a%20Bay%20Area%20growth%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Weinstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJenny%20Fielding%2C%20cofounder%20and%20managing%20partner%20at%20Everywhere%20Ventures%2C%20suspects%20Rock%20is%20a%20junior%20associate%20at%20a%20large%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20at%20a%20big%20firm%2C%20you're%20swapping%20deals%20with%20all%20the%20other%20associates%20at%20all%20the%20other%20firms%2C%26quot%3B%20Fielding%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey're%20the%20first%20eyes%20on%20all%20this%20stuff%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20a%20super%20senior%20person.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6d0d96f-23a1-4721-a23b-2c956ab92947%5C%22%3EFilling%20a%20void%20when%20startups%20are%20restricted%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20prohibits%20startups%20from%20publicizing%20when%20they%20are%20raising%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SEC's%20primary%20concern%20is%20protecting%20unsophisticated%20or%20inexperienced%20investors%20from%20being%20swept%20up%20in%20the%20hype%20of%20an%20investment%20opportunity%20they%20don't%20fully%20understand%20or%20that%20lacks%20sufficient%20disclosure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Steve%20Brotman%2C%20managing%20partner%20at%20Alpha%20Partners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20details%20about%20funding%20rounds%20are%20restricted%20to%20trusted%20circles%2C%20and%20founders%20might%20miss%20out%20on%20potential%20investors%2C%20Brotman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Arfur%20Rock%20is%20doing%20is%20essentially%20hacking%20the%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20enables%20fundraising%20information%20to%20leak%20anonymously.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERock%20says%20the%20account's%20information%20comes%20from%20founders%2C%20investors%2C%20employees%2C%20limited%20partners%2C%20and%20anonymous%20tipsters%2C%20and%20anything%20posted%20is%20already%20a%20%26quot%3Bknown%20secret%26quot%3B%20in%20Silicon%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20I%20share%20has%20been%20passed%20around%20the%20right%20dinners%2C%20parties%2C%20group%20chats%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20Rock%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20would%20never%20violate%20a%20non-disclosure%20agreement.%20%26quot%3BI%20take%20this%20seriously.%20They're%20sacrosanct.%20If%20I'm%20under%20one%2C%20it%20is%20followed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Rock%20posts%20nonpublic%20information%2C%20it%20is%20uniformly%20positive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20notice%20I%20don't%20post%20layoffs%2C%26quot%3B%20Rock%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20talk%20about%20firm%20departures.%20I%20don't%20talk%20about%20company%20scandals.%20I%20don't%20do%20down%20rounds.%20I%20don't%20share%20poor%20fund%20performances.%20I%20don't%20dunk%20on%20people.%20People%20constantly%20ask%20for%20or%20send%20me%20this%20kind%20of%20gossip.%20I%20want%20to%20spotlight%20some%20of%20what%20I%20consider%20the%20best%20among%20the%20current%20wave%20of%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20not%20criticize%20founders%2C%20investors%2C%20or%20my%20friends%20from%20behind%20a%20keyboard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22362a7cba-10a6-4333-a6c8-65acc541f46a%5C%22%3EIs%20anonymity%20a%20feature%20or%20a%20bug%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELeaks%20are%20leaks%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20nice%20they%20may%20be%2C%20and%20some%20question%20whether%20Rock%20is%20providing%20as%20much%20of%20a%20public%20service%20as%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatrick%20Collison%2C%20CEO%20of%20Stripe%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fpatrickc%2Fstatus%2F1930014955052384721%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecently%20asked%20on%20X%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BDo%20the%20companies%20consent%20to%20the%20leaks%3F%26quot%3B%20(Rock%20replied%20that%20people%20%26quot%3Bare%20often%20surprised%20how%20much%20of%20what%20I%20share%20is%20green%E2%80%91lit%20by%20the%20insiders%20themselves.%26quot%3B)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMenlo%20Ventures'%20Gong%20said%20Rock's%20posts%20can%20sometimes%20upend%20startups'%20carefully%20laid%20publicity%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20all%20for%20transparency%20that%20helps%20founders%2C%26quot%3B%20Gong%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20downside%20is%20when%20the%20account%20leaks%20info%20before%20the%20founder%20is%20ready%20to%20announce%2C%20they%20don't%20get%20the%20press%20coverage%20they%20were%20hoping%20for.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERock%20sometimes%20deletes%20posts%20without%20explanation%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20to%20track%20whether%20the%20posts%20are%20always%20accurate.%20Their%20mission%20of%20transparency%20is%20very%20much%20a%20one-way%20street%2C%20which%20Jay%20Kolbe%2C%20cofounder%20and%20senior%20managing%20partner%20of%20strategic%20communications%20firm%20Impact%20Partners%2C%20finds%20concerning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20downside%20of%20Arfur%20Rock%20isn't%20that%20it's%20opening%20a%20new%20channel%20for%20information%2C%20it's%20that%20we%20don't%20know%20the%20motives%20of%20those%20who%20are%20behind%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20how%20well-intended%20they%20may%20be%2C%20it%20lacks%20the%20necessary%20guardrails%20of%20proven%20channels%20and%20real%20reporting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJesse%20Middleton%2C%20general%20partner%20at%20Flybridge%20Capital%20Partners%2C%20says%20he%20finds%20Rock's%20account%20%26quot%3Bfascinating%26quot%3B%20but%20takes%20the%20information%20with%20a%20grain%20of%20salt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20clarity%20on%20who's%20running%20the%20account%20(and%20no%2C%20I%20don't%20know)%2