s%20are%20we%20ever%20thinking%20that%20we%20will%20get%20rid%20of%20our%20human%20workforce%20and%20do%20this%20just%20through%20AI%20agents%20or%20other%20things%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Raj%20Sharma%2C%20a%20global%20managing%20partner%20at%20EY%2C%20told%20me%20in%20a%20recent%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20problem%20is%20more%20about%20a%20%3Cem%3Elack%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20human%20employees.%20In%20a%20world%20where%20modern%20businesses%20operate%20across%20dozens%20of%20jurisdictions%20with%20complex%20and%20ever-changing%20regulations%2C%20audits%20have%20become%20a%20logistical%20and%20mental%20minefield.%20That%20complexity%20has%20driven%20some%20away%20from%20the%20field%2C%20contributing%20to%20a%20nationwide%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshortage-accountants-we-should-be-worried-recruit-young-talent-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccountant%20shortage%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2065%2C000%20students%20in%20the%20US%20completed%20bachelor's%20or%20master's%20degrees%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faccountant-shortage-sexy-taxes-business-school-pwc-kpmg-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaccounting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%202021-22%20school%20year%2C%2018%25%20fewer%20than%20a%20decade%20earlier.%20About%2030%2C000%20people%20took%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshortage-accountants-we-should-be-worried-recruit-young-talent-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECPA%3C%2Fa%3E%20exam%20in%202022%2C%20down%20roughly%2040%25%20from%202010.%20Meanwhile%2C%20three-quarters%20of%20CPAs%20in%20the%20US%20were%20thought%20to%20be%20at%20or%20near%20retirement%20in%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20American%20Institute%20of%20Certified%20Public%20Accountants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20AI%20can%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20things%2C%20think%20of%20our%20business%20around%20assurance%2C%20audit%2C%20and%20the%20certifications%20that%20are%20required.%20We%20are%20significantly%20short%20of%20people%20coming%20up%20with%20accounting%20degrees%2C%26quot%3B%20Sharma%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20still%20hiring%20big%20classes%20of%20accountants%20from%20colleges%2C%20and%20we%20are%20training%20them%20into%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEY%20is%20embedding%20this%20AI%20assistance%20across%20tax%2C%20risk%2C%20and%20finance%20workflows%20via%20its%20EY.ai%20Agentic%20Platform%2C%20developed%20and%20launched%20with%20Nvidia%20earlier%20this%20year.%20This%20has%20already%20created%20about%20200%20specialized%20AI%20agents%20that%20support%2080%2C000%20EY%20employees%20to%20help%20with%20tasks%20such%20as%20data%20collection%2C%20document%20analysis%2C%20and%20tax%20compliance%20%E2%80%94%20automating%20dull%20tasks%20and%20amplifying%20more%20engaging%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220dc166b1-9a8e-4b10-b03f-93005a1c4868%5C%22%3EMore%20interesting%2C%20less%20daunting%2C%20audits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESharma%20cited%20AI-powered%20audits%20as%20an%20example%20of%20what's%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAudits%20are%20a%20staple%20of%20accounting%20work%20that%20traditionally%20involved%20sampling%20a%20small%20subset%20of%20transactions%20to%20look%20for%20errors%20or%20fraud.%20This%20is%20painstaking%20work%2C%20and%20pretty%20daunting%20when%20you're%20checking%20the%20books%20of%20huge%2C%20complex%20multinational%20corporations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20overwhelming%20for%20our%20accountants%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20one%20big%20reason%20why%20people%20don't%20want%20to%20go%20into%20accounting%20because%20it's%20so%20technical%2C%20so%20deep.%20And%20the%20risks%20are%20so%20high%20of%20getting%20it%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20how%20AI%20can%20make%20these%20situations%20more%20manageable.%20For%20example%2C%20an%20audit%20that%20used%20to%20take%20five%20hours%20for%20a%20particular%20process%20might%20now%20take%20tw