ranz%20has%20spotlighted%20stories%20from%20everyone%20from%20a%20design%20intern%20for%20the%20National%20Park%20Service%20to%20a%20creative%20director%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-layoffs-job-cuts-document-impacted-teams-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20definitely%20think%20it's%20opening%20up%20people's%20eyes%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20a%20layoff%20is%20not%20this%20thing%20that%20happens%20to%20a%20certain%20type%20of%20person%20in%20a%20certain%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20Ehrenkranz%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20can%20happen%20to%20anyone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20visibility%20of%20layoffs%20doesn't%20make%20it%20any%20easier%20when%20a%20call%20with%20HR%20gets%20added%20to%20your%20calendar.%20Research%20published%20in%20the%20International%20Journal%20of%20Mental%20Health%20found%20that%20losing%20a%20job%20increased%20the%20risk%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tandfonline.com%2Fdoi%2Fabs%2F10.2753%2FIMH0020-7411390201%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edepression%2C%20risky%20substance%20use%2C%20and%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E.%20For%20Mustafa%2C%20being%20laid%20off%20meant%20involuntarily%20grinding%20his%20teeth%20at%20night%20and%20having%20debilitating%20stress%20headaches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChristine%20Reichenbach%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20her%20chief%20of%20staff%20role%20at%20the%20cloud%20computing%20company%20VMware%20in%20January%202024%20while%20she%20was%2034%20weeks%20pregnant.%20It%20quickly%20sent%20her%20into%20a%20downward%20spiral.%20She%20ended%20up%20on%20postpartum%20anxiety%20medication%20and%2C%20despite%20having%20ample%20savings%2C%20put%20her%20baby%20in%20day%20care%20at%20seven%20weeks%20to%20frantically%20hunt%20for%20a%20new%20job.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20very%20illogical%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20what%20it%20did%20to%20my%20brain.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Reichenbach%20was%20introduced%20to%20a%20Discord%20group%20called%20The%20Labor%20Club%2C%20a%20referral-only%20application-based%20group%20of%20500%20women%20who%20have%20experienced%20being%20laid%20off%20while%20pregnant%20or%20postpartum.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20specific%20niche%20that%20was%20just%20awful%20to%20experience%2C%26quot%3B%20Reichenbach%20says.%20Her%20husband%2C%20though%20supportive%2C%20couldn't%20relate%20to%20what%20she%20was%20going%20through.%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20no%20idea%20what%20it's%20like%20to%20be%20laid%20off%20pregnant.%26quot%3B%20Instead%2C%20she%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-girl-boss-women-musk-zuckerberg-dimon-alpha-male-backlash-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epool%20of%20women%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20turn%20to%20for%20both%20practical%20resources%20and%2C%20importantly%2C%20emotional%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20some%20soul-searching%2C%20Reichenbach%20decided%20to%20leave%20Big%20Tech%20altogether%20and%20founded%20her%20own%20company%2C%20The%20Phoenix%20Formula%2C%20at%20the%20start%20of%20this%20year%20with%20the%20goal%20of%20empowering%20other%20job%20seekers.%20She%20is%20also%20building%20her%20own%20support%20group%2C%20Beyond%20the%20Layoffs%2C%20on%20LinkedIn%20and%20Slack.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20need%20a%20space%20for%20this%20to%20actually%20be%20constructive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20If%20members%20need%20a%20space%20to%20yell%20in%20all%20caps%2C%20there's%20a%20channel%20for%20that.%20%26quot%3BI%20hope%20it's%20a%20place%20people%20can%20vent%20on%20a%20bad%20day%20and%20it's%20not%20on%20social%20media%20for%20hiring%20managers%20to%20see%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20stigma%20around%20layoffs%20disappears%2C%20the%20boundaries%20of%20professionalism%20on%20social%20media%20have%20become%20increasingly%20blurred.%20Ask%20any%20recruiter%2C%20and%20they'll%20say%20bad-mouthing%20a%20previous%20employer%20on%20social%20media%20is%20tantamount%20to%20career%20cyanide.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gives%20me%20alarm%20bells%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brad%20Thomas%2C%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fex-middle-manager-big-tech-flattening-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20business%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Orange%20Quarter%2C%20a%20tech%20recruitment%20company%20in%20New%20York.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20same%20as%20when%20a%20candidate%20interviews%20somewhere%20%E2%80%94%20talking%20bad%20in%20an%20unprofessional%20manner%20about%20a%20previous%20employer%20is%20just%20not%20a%20good%20look.%26quot%3B%20His%20advice%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20posting%20on%20social%20media%20is%20to%20keep%20it%20professional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20new%20culture%20of%20layoffs%2C%20however%2C%20there%20is%20an%20important%20caveat.%20%26quot%3BThe%20size%20of%20the%20company%20makes%20a%20difference%2C%26quot%3B%20Thomas%20explains.%20%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20has%20a%20pop%20at%20Meta%20or%20Google%2C%20it's%20less%20personal%20and%20less%20damaging%20to%20the%20brand%20versus%20a%20startup%20of%2030%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20when%20Meta%20let%20go%20of%20some%204%2C000%20workers%2C%20branding%20them%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-low-performers-zuckerberg-linkedin-job-searching-social-media-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow%20performers%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20on%20the%20way%20out%2C%20the%20departing%20employees%20refused%20to%20leave%20quietly%2C%20pushing%20back%20on%20the%20label%20on%20LinkedIn.%20As%20Business%20Insider's%20Aki%20Ito%20wrote%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20something%20we%20haven't%20seen%20before%20in%20the%20professional%20world%3A%20Employees%20sticking%20up%20for%20themselves%20in%20public%2C%20and%20calling%20out%20their%20former%20employer%20for%20misrepresenting%20their%20work.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20the%20private%20communities%20offer%20a%20kind%20of%20testimony%20that%20shifts%20blame%20from%20the%20employee%20back%20onto%20the%20employer.%20Ehrenkranz%20has%20had%20many%20people%20tell%20her%20that%20being%20interviewed%20for%20Laid%20Off%20or%20filling%20out%20her%20surveys%20is%20a%20cathartic%20experience.%20%26quot%3BA%20layoff%20these%20days%20is%20a%2010-minute%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzoom-layoffs-tech-eric-yuan-pay-cut-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZoom%20call%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20shut%20your%20computer%2C%20and%20then%20you're%20thrown%20into%20this%20new%20chapter%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20dedicated%20space%20to%20talk%20about%20being%20laid%20off%20with%20those%20who%20get%20it%20is%20a%20relief%20for%20Mustafa.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20really%20feel%20like%20I'm%20being%20pushy%20or%20shoving%20my%20layoff%20experiences%20down%20someone's%20throat%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20power%20in%20numbers%2C%20for%20some%2C%20those%20numbers%20can%20be%20overwhelming.%20A%20friend%20of%20Mustafa's%20left%20the%20Discord%20group%20shortly%20after%20joining.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20getting%20emotionally%20burned%20out%20from%20hearing%20about%20layoffs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explains.%20%26quot%3BShe's%20fortunately%20a%20freelance%20writer%2C%20so%20she's%20making%20some%20money.%20She%20can%20just%20tune%20out%20that%20stuff%20if%20she%20wants%20to.%20For%20me%2C%20I'm%20still%20desperately%20tuned%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEhrenkranz%20focuses%20on%20making%20sure%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELaid%20Off%20community%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20toxic-positivity-free%20zone.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20say%20the%20vibe%20is%20just%20real%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20no%20'Everything%20happens%20for%20a%20reason'%20or%20'You'll%20get%20the%20next%20one.'%20People%20don't%20want%20to%20hear%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20just%20a%20place%20to%20wallow%2C%20many%20of%20these%20support%20groups%20are%20designed%20as%20both%20a%20safety%20net%20and%20a%20springboard%20for%20when%20members%20are%20ready%20to%20begin%20the%20hunt%20for%20their%20next%20role.%20Fana%20Yohannes%2C%20a%20social%20media%20consultant%20and%20former%20Meta%20employee%2C%20founded%20the%20group%20Here2Help%20to%20give%20job%20seekers%20a%20leg%20up.%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%202020%20layoffs%2C%20she%20posted%20on%20Instagram%20that%20she%20was%20open%20to%20reviewing%20and%20providing%20feedback%20on%20five%20people's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flanded-dream-job-using-chatgpt-write-resume-cover-letter-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Er%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BOne%20person%20replied%20and%20was%20like%2C%20actually%2C%20I'd%20be%20down%20to%20help%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20From%20there%2C%20Yohannes%20says%2C%20Here2Help%20grew%20to%20200%20mentors%20who%20helped%20about%202%2C000%20people%20find%20new%20opportunities%20during%20COVID.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20come%20to%20an%20era%20where%20layoffs%20are%20part%20of%20the%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Yohannes%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20kind%20of%20be%20strategic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20four%20months%20of%20sending%20out%20applications%2C%20Mustafa%20has%20a%20second%20interview%20lined%20up%20for%20another%20tech%20role.%20Even%20if%20he%20gets%20the%20job%2C%20he%20plans%20on%20staying%20in%20the%20Laid%20Off%20community%20for%20a%20while%20%E2%80%94%20just%20in%20case.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floyalty-employee-employer-job-security-broken-work-companies-bosses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrust%20these%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20anymore%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says%20about%20employers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel