2750%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERubrik%20cofounder%20and%20CEO%20Bipul%20Sinha.%3Cp%3ERubrik%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20the%20first%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20building%20the%20company%2C%20Rubrik's%20CEO%20opened%20board%20meetings%20to%20all%20staff.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBipul%20Sinha%20said%20as%20many%20as%20800%20staff%20members%20tuned%20in%20to%20these%20meetings.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20data%20management%20firm%20went%20public%20in%20April%202024%20and%20is%20worth%20%2419%20billion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20CEOs%20keep%20board%20meetings%20private.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20for%20the%20first%20seven%20to%20eight%20years%20of%20building%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frubrik-funding-33-billion-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edata%20management%20firm%20Rubrik%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bipul%20Sinha%20let%20every%20employee%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20put%20the%20board%20meeting%20in%20a%20large%20conference%20room%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CEO%20and%20cofounder%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20Logan%20Bartlett%20Show%26quot%3B%20published%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BWe%20let%20people%20sit%20on%20the%20ground%20if%20needed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20could%20ask%20questions%2C%20so%20it%20was%20not%20a%20webinar%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20Sinha%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20had%20situations%20where%20people%20actually%20asked%20hard%20questions%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20board%20meeting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20many%20as%20800%20staff%20members%20tuned%20in%20to%20some%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethese%20sessions%2C%20Sinha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20direct%20result%20of%20this%20idea%20of%20transparency%20that%20really%20created%20alignment%20and%20velocity%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20venture%20partner%20at%20Lightspeed%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20knew%20where%20we%20are%20going%20and%20what%20ne