esort-sumba-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eisland%20of%20Sumba%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20friend.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bd1ebca1-9f8a-491e-be79-1a5f2633248b%5C%22%3EOverpopulation%20was%20no%20longer%20a%20problem%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESumba%20is%20a%2090-minute%20direct%20flight%20from%20Denpasar%20International%20Airport.%20It's%20about%20twice%20the%20size%20of%20Bali%2C%20has%20one-sixth%20of%20Bali's%20population%2C%20and%20a%20fraction%20of%20its%20tourists.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20known%20for%20limited%20WiFi%20and%20cell%20service%20across%20large%20swaths%20of%20its%20undeveloped%20territory.%20There's%20no%20signage%20on%20the%20main%20roads%20indicating%20the%20island's%20scenic%20spots%2C%20making%20it%20hard%20for%20visitors%20to%20find%20them%20without%20a%20local%20guide.%20We%20hired%20a%20guide%20my%20friend%20found%20through%20Facebook%2C%20and%20we're%20glad%20we%20did.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Woman%20standing%20in%20a%20bikini%20under%20a%20waterfall%20in%20Sumba%2C%20Indonesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68426ed39d73a0031e8e0095%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221620%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20visited%20sandy%20coves%20and%20waterfalls%20in%20Sumba.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESumba's%20natural%20beauty%20lived%20up%20to%20our%20expectations.%20The%20rock-framed%20sandy%20coves%2C%20the%20turquoise%20lagoon%2C%20the%20landscapes%20of%20velvety%20green%20hills%2C%20and%20the%20waterfalls%20left%20my%20friend%20and%20me%20in%20awe.%20We%20were%20charmed%20by%20goats%20lounging%20by%20the%20side%20of%20the%20road%20and%20by%20horses%20meandering%20across%20expanses%20of%20golden%20savannah.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20we%20had%20the%20sights%20all%20to%20ourselves.%20Sometimes%2C%20groups%20of%20local%20kids%20would%20come%20over%20to%20talk%20to%20us.%20The%20roads%20were%20free%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Horses%20near%20the%20Puru%20Kambera%20Savannah%2C%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20Sumba%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68429839c19ab3675c10c79c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHorses%20were%20spotted%20near%20the%20Puru%20Kambera%20Savannah%20on%20the%20eastern%20side%20of%20Sumba%20Island.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20absence%20of%20tourists%20and%20traffic%20came%20the%20absence%20of%20extensive%20food%20and%20massage%20options%2C%20which%20we%20had%20grown%20accustomed%20to%20in%20Bali.%20I%20never%20found%20wine%20or%20cocktails%20anywhere%20in%20Sumba%2C%20though%20I%20imagine%20they're%20available%20at%20the%20handful%20of%205-star%20hotels%20on%20the%20island.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-people-on-this-remote-indonesian-island-still-practice-blood-sacrifice-2015-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epeople%20in%20Sumba%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20speak%20much%20English%2C%20including%20our%20guide%2C%20so%20we%20needed%20translation%20apps%20to%20communicate%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20When%20there%20was%20no%20cell%20service%2C%20we%20had%20to%20resort%20to%20hand%20gestures.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20punctuality%3F%20We%20found%20out%20that%20it's%20not%20a%20thing%20in%20Sumba.%20Our%20driver%20tended%20to%20show%20up%2015%20to%2020%20minutes%20after%20our%20agreed%20departure%20time%2C%20then%20order%20himself%20a%20coffee%20before%20we%20left%2C%20then%20stop%20to%20pick%20up%20his%20breakfast%20at%20a%20roadside%20shop%20or%20get%20gas.%20He%20was%20an%20excellent%20drone%20videographer%20and%20photographer%2C%20though%2C%20which%20helped%20make%20up%20for%20his%20relaxed%20sense%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae969d8c-e985-40ac-ab54-ebe960a7ac2e%5C%22%3EA%20true%20mental%20reset%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20four-day%20guided%20Sumba%20road%20trip%20covered%20a%20lot%20of%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20road%20trip%2C%20we%20spent%20three%20nights%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkoh-samui-beach-hotel-cielo-owner-thailand-renovate-raise-family-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboutique%20hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20a%20deserted%20stretch%20of%20white%20sand%20beach%20in%20East%20Sumba%2C%20about%20an%20hour%20from%20the%20airport%2C%20and%20it%20was%20there%20that%20we%20found%20total%20relaxation.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShaded%20by%20tall%20cemara%20trees%2C%20the%20temperature%20was%20perfect%20both%20day%20and%20night.%20We%20were%20lulled%20to%20sleep%20every%20night%20by%20the%20sound%20of%20gentle%20ocean%20waves%20lapping%20the%20shore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a.%20red%20bikini%20floating%20in%20the%20Waikuri%20Lagoon%20in%20Sumbai%2C%20Indonesia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68426f95c19ab3675c10c73c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20friend%20floating%20in%20the%20Waikuri%20Lagoon.%3Cp%3ESonya%20Moore%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20hotel%2C%20Cemara%20Beachfront%20Suite%2C%20was%20%2480%20per%20night%20and%20came%20with%20great%20service.%20The%20staff%20brought%20us%20tea%20with%20little%20desserts%20every%20afternoon%20and%20were%20always%20ready%20to%20provide%20any%20extras%20we%20asked%20for%20to%20make%20our%20stay%20more%20enjoyable.%20Except%20wine.%20Next%20time%2C%20I'd%20bring%20a%20bottle%20or%20two%20in%20my%20suitcase%2C%20along%20with%20a%20good%20book.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attentive%20care%20of%20the%20staff%20and%20the%20idyllic%20setting%20allowed%20us%20to%20completely%20unwind%20and%20fully%20enjoy%20just%20being%20there.%20We%20cou