EThe%20impact%20on%20local%20communities%20was%20just%20as%20devastating%20%E2%80%94%20polluted%20water%2C%20ravaged%20landscapes%2C%20and%20disrupted%20lives.%20This%20eye-opening%20experience%20led%20to%20a%20fundamental%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CCan%20you%20build%20without%20using%20these%20materials%3F%20Or%20can%20you%20build%20without%20scraping%20out%20too%20many%20resources%20from%20the%20planet%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20concrete%20conundrum%3A%20beauty%20or%20beast%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Krithika%2C%20the%20answer%20was%20a%20resounding%20yes.%20And%20her%20gaze%20fell%20squarely%20on%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20culprits%20in%20mainstream%20construction%3A%20concrete.%20%E2%80%9CConcrete%20was%20not%20designed%20for%20residential%20structures%2C%20but%20for%20it%20to%20take%20up%20the%20mass%20vibration%20of%20industrial%20units%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mince%20her%20words%20about%20its%20environmental%20footprint.%20%E2%80%9CA%20single%20bag%20of%20cement%20uses%20around%2025%20litres%20of%20fresh%20water%2C%20even%20if%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20dry%20manufacturing%20unit.%20And%20just%20one%20tonne%20of%20cement%20is%20needed%20to%20build%20a%20500%20square%20foot%20room%2C%20which%20releases%20around%20one%20tonne%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20into%20the%20air%2C%E2%80%9D%20Krithika%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20the%20overall%20carbon%20footprint%20of%20such%20structures%20are%20extremely%20high.%20%E2%80%9CBeyond%20that%2C%20concrete%20absorbs%20a%20lot%20of%20heat%20during%20the%20day%20and%20re-radiates%20it%20at%20night.%20That%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20t