3Egender%20dysphoria.%3C%2Fem%3E%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20about%20being%20confused%20%E2%80%94%20it%20is%20about%20the%20emotional%20discomfort%20or%20distress%20that%20can%20come%20from%20that%20mismatch.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20someone%20might%20strongly%20wish%20to%20be%20seen%20and%20treated%20as%20a%20different%20gender%2C%20or%20they%20might%20feel%20deeply%20uncomfortable%20with%20their%20body%20because%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20reflect%20who%20they%20are%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESide%20note%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIt%20is%20important%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20not%20all%20transgender%20or%20nonbinary%20people%20experience%20gender%20dysphoria%2C%20and%20those%20who%20do%20aren%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%9Cbroken!%E2%80%9D%20They%E2%80%99re%20simply%20trying%20to%20live%20in%20a%20world%20that%20often%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20them.%20What%20matters%20most%20is%20supporting%20each%20person%E2%80%99s%20journey%20with%20respect%2C%20kindness%2C%20and%20understanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-7-1749190053.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nonbinary%20is%20an%20umbrella%20term%20that%20encompasses%20various%20identities%2C%20including%20agender%2C%20bigender%2C%20and%20demigender.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-7-1749190053.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-7-1749190053-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-7-1749190053-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FTBI-featured-image-7-1749190053-768x402.jpg%20768w