2022%2C%20they%20had%20a%20physical%20presence.%20There%2C%20he%20met%20Mohit%20Kumar%20Nayak%2C%20a%20Computer%20Science%20student%20at%20KIT%20University%2C%20Bhubaneshwar%2C%20who%20shared%20his%20dream.%20In%20a%20funny%20hostel%20encounter%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CWe%20met%20in%20the%20washroom!%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Mohit%2C%20they%20found%20common%20ground%20and%20an%20immense%20love%20towards%20the%20realm%20of%20space%2C%20and%20decided%20to%20build%20something%20monumental%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20initial%20team%20swelled%20to%2030%2C%20reality%20soon%20hit%3A%20job%20security%20and%20financial%20concerns%20led%20most%20members%20to%20opt%20for%20traditional%20careers.%20Only%20a%20core%20group%20of%20four%20remained%2C%20determined%20to%20stay%20the%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20CubeSats%20affordably%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20decided%20to%20work%20on%20the%20theoretical%20part%20of%20building%20%E2%80%98CubeSats%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20miniature%20satellites%20typically%20used%20for%20research%2C%20that%20would%20specialise%20in%20detecting%20gamma%20radiation.%20This%20niche%20was%20important%3A%20Gamma%20rays%20hold%20the%20key%20to%20understanding%20phenomena%20like%20black%20holes%20and%20cosmic%20explosions.%20Yet%20India%20had%20no%20CubeSat%20dedicated%20to%20this%20field.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20wanted%20to%20focus%20on%20making%20CubeSats%2C%20because%20they%20will%20be%20efficient%2C%20where%20the%20size%20would%20be%20tiny%20compared%20to%20a%20conventional%20satellite.%20With%20the%20subsequent%20development%20of%20nano-technology%2C%20developing%20this%20is%20reliable%20and%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20approach%20to%20building%20was%20radically%20different.%20Instead%20of%20buying%20parts%20from%20expensive%20aerospace%20vendors%2C%20they%20sourced%20local%20materials.%20%E2%80%9CAluminium%207075%2C%20used%20to%20make%20satellites%2C%20would%20normally%20cost%20%24180%2C000%20through%20a%20space%20supplier%2C%20but%20could%20be%20found%20for%20Rs%20700%20at%20a%20local%20metal%20shop%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Snehadeep%2C%20who%20realised%20through%20intense%20R%26amp%3BD.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCFIGuoScTO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCFIGuoScTO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FDCFIGuoScTO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Nebula%20Space%20Organisation%20(%40nebulaspaceorg)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20monopoly%20in%20space%20manufacturing.%20We%20realised%20we%20could%20bypass%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Snehadeep.%20They%20cut%20the%20metal%20using%20CNC%20machines%2C%20ensuring%20precision%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20prototypes%20are%20modular%20and%20plug-and-play%2C%20almost%20like%20Lego%20sets.%20Controlled%20via%20a%20smartphone%20app%2C%20these%20CubeSats%20would%20provide%20real-time%20gamma%20radiation%20data%2C%20and%20even%20live%20camera%20feeds%20from%20orbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManufacturing%20locally%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20saving%20money.%20It%20was%20a%20statement%3A%20space%20should%20not%20be%20limited%20to%20billion-dollar%20organisations.%20Their%20project%20showed%20that%20with%20innovation%20and%20resourcefulness%2C%20even%20college%20students%20could%20break%20into%20the%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCreating%20our%20structures%20and%20PCBs%20allows%20us%20to%20be%20self-reliant%2C%20while%20also%20making%20it%20at%20a%20significantly%20lower%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Mohit%2C%20whose%20method%20will%20reduce%20the%20expense%20by%20125%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETrash%20%E2%80%94%20even%20a%20problem%20in%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Snehadeep%20and%20Mohit%20are%20deeply%20conscious%20of%20another%20looming%20crisis%3A%20space%20debris.%20%E2%80%9CAryabhata%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20satellite%2C%20launched%20in%201975%2C%20is%20now%20space%20junk.%20No%20one%20even%20knows%20where%20it%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Snehadeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Nebula%E2%80%99s%20CubeSats%20can%20be%20designed%20with%20an%20end-of-life%20plan.%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20solar%20sails%20%E2%80%94%20thin%2C%20reflective%20surfaces%20that%20harness%20the%20sun%E2%80%99s%20photon%20energy%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can%20deorbit%20after%20completing%20their%20mission.%20Instead%20of%20cluttering%20Earth%E2%80%99s%20orbit%2C%20the%20CubeSats%20would%20glide%20back%20into%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20disintegrate%20safely%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains