hecked%20by%20scientists%2C%20but%20making%20the%20final%20product%20is%20a%20big%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20put%20it%20into%20context%2C%20right%20now%2C%20people%20are%20venturing%20into%206G%20and%20researching%20it%2C%20but%20how%20to%20include%206G%20in%20individual%20phones%20is%20a%20huge%20challenge%2C%20which%20requires%20frequent%20testing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20of%20four%20has%20submitted%20their%20research%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffirst-space-tourist-from-india-gopi-thotakura-shorts-spacetourism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emultiple%20international%20bodies%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20their%20paper%20was%20accepted%20at%20the%20International%20Astronautical%20Congress%202024%20in%20Milan%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20milestones%20for%20any%20emerging%20space%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22illustration%20of%20the%20satellite.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T192033.482-1749045168-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FMervin-Feature-image-2025-06-04T1