beSats%20and%20interplanetary%20missions%2C%20offering%20affordable%2C%20sustainable%20satellite%20technology%20to%20governments%20and%20private%20players%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20Government%20or%20an%20organisation%20has%20a%20Rs%2010%20million%20budget%20for%20100%20satellites%2C%20that%20will%20be%20a%20boost%20for%20them.%20If%20you%20compare%20the%20cost%20of%20NASA%2C%20which%20is%20500%20million%20dollars%20per%20year%2C%20this%20is%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20Snehadeep%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20need%20mentors%20who%20are%20well-versed%20in%20both%20Physics%20and%20engineering%20to%20guide%20us%20long-term.%20And%20the%20best%20mentors%20are%20from%20ISRO%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Snehadeep%2C%20highlighting%20the%20potential%20for%20India%20to%20succeed%20in%20the%20space%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20see%20space%20as%20the%20final%20frontier%20reserved%20for%20billion-dollar%20corporations%20and%20elite%20scientists%2C%20Snehadeep%20and%20Mohit%20believe%20otherwise.%20They%20are%20proof%20that%20innovation%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20need%20sprawling%20labs%20or%20massive%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20you%20need%20a%20pen%20and%20paper%20to%20become%20a%20theoretical%20scientist%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Snehadeep.%20As%20they%20gear%20up%20to%20test%20the%20prototype%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20gamma-ray%20CubeSat%2C%20built%20by%20students%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20not%20just%20reaching%20for%20the%20stars%20%E2%80%94%20they%E2%80%99re%20building%20a%20bridge%20so%20that%20countless%20others%20can%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Vidya%20Gowri%20Venkatesh%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnebulaspaceorg%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENebula%20Space%20Organization.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1749183838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22http