ed%20funds%20with%20local%20Rogi%20Kalyan%20Samitis.%20These%20are%20patient%20welfare%20committees%20enabled%20by%20the%20NHM%20(National%20Health%20Mission)%20that%20act%20as%20trustees%20for%20hospitals%20and%20health%20centres.%20They%20are%20free%20to%20prescribe%2C%20generate%2C%20and%20use%20their%20funds%20as%20per%20their%20judgment%20for%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20and%20maintenance%20of%20the%20services.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EE4H%20DRE%20systems%20have%20a%20standard%20built-in%20autonomy%20of%20two%20to%20three%20days%2C%20but%20if%20we%20implement%20them%20in%20an%20area%20with%20very%20heavy%20rainfall%20or%20high%20cloud%20cover%2C%20we%20extend%20it%20to%20five%20to%20six%20days.%20If%20our%20systems%20can%20function%20well%20in%20Meghalaya%E2%80%99s%20Cherrapunji%20(Sohra)%2C%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20wettest%20places%2C%20then%20they%20can%20work%20anywhere.%20We%20have%20collaborated%20with%20the%20state%20governments%20to%20ensure%20that%20when%20they%20procure%20new%20equipment%2C%20like%20baby%20warmers%2C%20oxygen%20concentrators%2C%20and%20freezers%2C%20they%20acquire%20the%20most%20energy-efficient%20appliances%20available.%20This%20could%20potentially%20result%20in%20reduction%20in%20energy%20requirement%20by%2060%25%20to%2080%25.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20installing%20the%20systems%2C%20however%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20imperative%20that%20the%20staff%20at%20these%20health%20centres%20fully%20understand%20the%20system%20and%20its%20benefits.%20What%20follows%20is%20a%20training%20process%20for%20the%20staff%20to%20operate%20and%20maintain%20the%20system%20so%20that%20they%20can%20take%20ownership%20of%20it%20down%20the%20line.%C2%A0%3